v1.9.14-01
 In compliance with the latest Google privacy standards, Cadpage will no longer access your email account information without your explicit permission. Cadpage only needs this account information to resolve occasional subscription issues. If Cadpage believes it needs email account information to maintain your existing payment status, you will have already been asked for your consent to retrieve this information.
